      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">ETRON: Inflation-Proof Green Investments</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-8">
        Introducing ETRON, a novel stablecoin backed by the real-world performance of renewable energy markets. This innovative financial
